commit.message: Add support for the new Indic_Conjunct_Break property.

Support for the new IDS_Unary_Operator property and…

Rename Cjk.is_ids_tri_op to Cjk.is_ids_trinary_operator.

Closes #23.
Let Uucp.unicode_version be defined by the UCD.
